"The <strong>CRM module</strong> helps construction companies capture leads "
"from multiple\n"
"            sources, track communications, and schedule follow-ups.  <br/"
">You can prioritize\n"
"            high-value opportunities and turn inquiries into profitable "
"projects."
msgstr ""
"Le <strong>module CRM</strong> aide les entreprises de construction à capter "
"des leads provenant de multiples\n"
"        sources, à suivre les communications et à planifier les suivis.  "
"<br/>Vous pouvez prioriser\n"
"        les opportunités à forte valeur et transformer les demandes en "
"projets rentables."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Planning App</strong> with its field service capabilities helps "
"you manage on-site interventions such as\n"
"            follow-up works, warranty services, or urgent client requests. "
"Technicians can access\n"
"            tasks, log hours, and report outcomes directly from their mobile "
"devices."
msgstr ""
"L'<strong>app Planification</strong> avec ses fonctionnalités de Services "
"sur Site vous aide à gérer les interventions sur site telles que\n"
"        les travaux de suivi, les services de garantie ou les demandes "
"urgentes des clients. Les techniciens peuvent accéder aux\n"
"        tâches, enregistrer leurs heures et rapporter les résultats "
"directement depuis leurs appareils mobiles."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Planning app</strong> schedules tasks, allocates employees, and "
"coordinates\n"
"            equipment use across multiple construction sites."
msgstr ""
"L'<strong>app Planification</strong> planifie les tâches, affecte les "
"employés et coordonne\n"
"        l'utilisation des équipements sur plusieurs chantiers."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Projects App</strong> allows you to manage tasks, assign "
"resources, and\n"
"            create milestones for each construction project."
msgstr ""
"L'app <strong>Projets</strong> vous permet de gérer les tâches, d'affecter "
"des ressources et\n"
"        de créer des jalons pour chaque projet de construction."

#. module: construction
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:construction.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Sales App</strong> enables rapid creation of professional "
"quotations.\n"
"            You can use product kits for materials, apply discounts, and "
"send polished proposals\n"
"            directly to clients."
msgstr ""
